标题：花冠、花圈（garland）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：στέμμα</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：stemma)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:13\">ACT 14:13</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>花冠是一种羊毛制成的花环，可能会加上叶子和花，缠绕在一根权杖上，或是编成一个圆圈戴在头上。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>花冠是古代异教神明崇拜仪式的重要用品。比如在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:13\">ACT 14:13</a> 中提到，人们把花披覆在准备献祭的牲畜身上。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:13\">ACT 14:13</a> 中，“花冠”可以译为“叶子做成的圆”、“花朵做成的环”，或“花朵做成的圈”。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
